  WHEN OPT-201-Organization-TouchPoint is present
  ASSERT every text:$x in OPT-201-Organization-TouchPoint satisfies (($x in OPT-301-Lot-AddInfo) or ($x in OPT-301-Lot-DocProvider) or ($x in OPT-301-Lot-EmployLegis) or ($x in OPT-301-Lot-EnvironLegis) or ($x in OPT-301-Lot-FiscalLegis) or ($x in OPT-301-Lot-Mediator) or ($x in OPT-301-Lot-ReviewInfo) or ($x in OPT-301-Lot-ReviewOrg) or ($x in OPT-301-Lot-TenderEval) or ($x in OPT-301-Lot-TenderReceipt) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-AddInfo) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-DocProvider) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-EmployLegis) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-EnvironLegis) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-FiscalLegis) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-Mediator) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-ReviewInfo) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-ReviewOrg) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-TenderEval) or ($x in OPT-301-Part-TenderReceipt) or ($x in BT-808-Review) or ($x in BT-807-Review))
